# 2D mass-transport test (Stage 8): same 100x50 mm rectangle as
# 2DRectQhull. The converter pipeline emits latticemt2D elements (one
# per Voronoi edge inside the rect) instead of lattice2D. Identical
# generator-side mesh is reused; the TM-vs-SM split happens in the
# converter via the `#@grid 2dTM` directive in the matching control.in.
#@output nodes.dat
#@domain 2
#@diam 0.008
#@maxiter 100000
#@perflag 2 0 0
#@ranint -1
#@ranflag 1
#@vertex 1 coords 2 -0.01 -0.01 refine 1. radius 0.
#@vertex 2 coords 2  0.11  0.06 refine 1. radius 0.
#@controlvertex 1 coords 2 0.0  0.025
#@controlvertex 2 coords 2 0.10 0.025
#@rect 1 box 4 0. 0. 0.10 0.05 refine 1.
